        <headline>Special Weather Statement issued September 18 at 2:07PM CDT by NWS Shreveport LA</headline>
        <description>At 207 PM CDT, Doppler radar was tracking a strong thunderstorm near
Wilkerson, or 10 miles north of Mount Pleasant, moving east at 10
mph.

HAZARD...Half inch size hail.

SOURCE...Radar indicated.

IMPACT...Minor damage to outdoor objects is possible.

Locations impacted include...
Wilkerson.
</description>
        <instruction>Monitor the weather situation closely and be alert for threatening
weather conditions.</instruction>
